Astrophysics [1] ( http://www.astropy.org/ ); Data manipulation [33] ( http://pandas.pydata.org/ ); Machine learning [37] ( http://scikit-learn.org/ ); Mathematics [46] ( http://www.sagemath.org/ ); Visualisation [17] ( http://matplotlib.org/ ); Furthermore, in [18] Python is described as an appropriate language for the reproduc- tion of Iterated Prisoner's Dilemma tournaments due to its object oriented nature and readability.
